    <string formatted="false" name="about_instructions">Billicity helps you estimate your monthly electricity bill based on Malaysian electricity tariff rates.\n\nFeatures:\n• Calculate bills using tiered rates\n• Apply rebate discounts (0%–5%)\n• Save and view calculation history\n• Edit or delete past records</string>
