    <string formatted="false" name="instructions">How to use:\n1. Select a month from the dropdown.\n2. Enter the electricity units used (1–1000 kWh).\n3. Adjust the rebate slider (0%–5%).\n4. Tap Calculate to see results.\n\nResults are automatically saved to history.</string>
