    <string formatted="false" name="usage_guide">HOW TO USE\n\n1. Select a month and enter your electricity usage (kWh).\n2. Adjust the rebate slider if applicable.\n3. Tap \"Calculate\" to see your estimated bill.\n4. Your result is saved automatically.\n5. Tap \"View History\" to see past calculations.\n6. Tap any record to view, edit, or delete it.</string>
